data.description: Beautiful updated home with a fabulous wrap around porch. You will love the outdoor living space perfect for BBQ'S with friends and family. The home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, large living room, indoor laundry room, office down stairs with a wrought iron arch gate. One bedroom downstairs with French doors that exit to rear deck. Gas fireplace in living room The other 2 rooms are upstairs with updated bathroom. New flooring and exterior paint. Close to All Sports Park.
